706387f-a.title: Brooklyn: Prospect Park West - 1st Street
706387f-a.text:
Prospect Park West, west side, from, but not including 1st Street, to and including Garfield Place. The vacant lot was the former home of Peter Winchester Rouss, a New York merchant.

August 2, 1928

P. L. Sperr.

http://www.beyondthegildedage.com/2012/01/peter-w-rouss-residence.html
